title: Jazz coach/possible supervillain Quin Snyder called out his entire team
text:
Jazz coach/possible supervillain Quin Snyder called out his entire team USA Today Sports 6 hrs ago Nina Mandell © Provided by USA Today Sports Jeff Swinger-USA TODAY Sports The Utah Jazz lost to the Oklahoma City Thunder by 11 on Tuesday in the team’s penultimate preseason game and when asked a question about Rudy Gobert, Jazz coach Quin Snyder took the opportunity to get some things off his chest.
AdChoices Quin Snyder was asked if he wants to see Rudy Gobert get it going before the season starts. This epic Quote: ensued: pic.twitter.com/Fxbdp9Pyv0
— Jody Genessy (@DJJazzyJody) October 21, 2015
In related news, Quin Snyder is terrifying.
